txt.en: The Orc encampment of Mokh Darga is a place of danger that has long troubled the Great Alliance.
Mokh Darga can be found in Parth Daenath.\n\nYou should defeat enemies at Mokh Darga.
Mokh Darga can be found in Parth Daenath.\n\nYou should defeat enemies at Mokh Darga.

The Orc encampment of Mokh Darga is not well fortified, but this speaks all the louder of the ferocity of its inhabitants. You should defeat any foes you come across while in Mokh Darga, and quiet the whispers.
Defeat trolls or gertheryg at Mokh Darga ([placeholder]/[placeholder])

The Orc encampment of Mokh Darga is a place of fierce foes and vile undertakings.
You have defeated many foes at Mokh Darga and helped to quiet the hushed whispers that speak of its inhabitants' ferocity.
